#. type: delimited block -
#: HandBook.adoc:1158
#, no-wrap
msgid "mount /dev/sda3 /mnt\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: HandBook.adoc:1164
msgid "If Slint's root file system is btrfs (as indicated by the output of \"lsblk\")  you need to mount it using the options mentioned in its /etc/fstab."
